WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
This is a deliberately constructed demo case. ScopeProof uses deterministic evidence rules and human review; it does not guarantee correctness or replace QA.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
The source owner confirms normalized acceptance criteria before analysis. ScopeProof does not invent product intent.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Deterministic rules cite implementation and test candidates—or state exactly what evidence is missing.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:50.000
A human decides what the evidence means. Static candidates are never presented as runtime verification.

00:00:50.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Record one honest outcome. ScopeProof supports the review; it does not guarantee correctness or replace QA.
